game features
-------------

- a playable game (v1.0)
  - lots of levels! Remove this TODO note at 20.

- v2 map builder
  - levels are graphs of squarish areas monged together
    - make sure exits line up and are blockage free
    - make sure there are "paths" between exits within a node e.g. earth/space/diamond
    - eggs don't get placed on walls

- sounds: tone.js
  - diamong ting
  - earth pffft
  - boulder landing chhhk
  - egg landing puhk
  - monster squashing bzzt
  - spirit caging ping
  - disable sounds in toolbar/keyboard

